00:00:09.931 --> 00:00:15.637 position:21% line:71% align:start
 <i>With Hong's bacteria</i>
 <i>circulating, the fate of Earth</i>
 <i>falls on the shoulders of the</i>
 <i>Annex 1 crew.</i>

00:00:15.670 --> 00:00:20.742 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>Keiji, locked in brutal combat</i>
 <i>with Xi, refuses to abandon</i>
 <i>principle,</i>

00:00:20.775 --> 00:00:23.779 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>regardless of the steep odds</i>
 <i>and violent blows he faces.</i>

00:00:23.813 --> 00:00:27.149 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>His endurance stems from a</i>
 <i>deep sense of obligation.</i>

00:00:27.183 --> 00:00:33.190 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>Keiji does not intend to kill</i>
 <i>his foe, and wishes no ill will</i>
 <i>upon any human combatant.</i>

00:00:33.223 --> 00:00:37.928 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>Rather, Keiji's suffering offer</i>
 <i>to buy more time for Wolf and</i>
 <i>the others to reach the</i>

00:00:37.961 --> 00:00:42.966 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>communications room, and notify</i>
 <i>Earth of their dire situation.</i>

00:00:53.911 --> 00:00:57.181 position:35% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Joseph)</i>
 <i>If Wolf can successfully hack</i>
 <i>into the radio tower, we can</i>

00:00:57.215 --> 00:01:01.719 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>re-establish communication with</i>
 <i>Earth and tell them about Squad</i>
 <i>4's treachery.</i>

00:01:01.752 --> 00:01:03.222 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>They'll send help,</i>

00:01:03.255 --> 00:01:06.959 position:10% line:77% align:start
Then we'll regroup with the
other survivors and finally
return to Earth

00:01:10.996 --> 00:01:15.300 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>Which is why I must ensure</i>
 <i>nothing gets in our way.</i>

00:01:15.334 --> 00:01:16.869 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'm heading for Liu.

00:01:16.902 --> 00:01:21.241 position:5% line:77% align:start
Once he realizes you've escaped,
he won't hesitate to fire
another missile...

00:01:21.274 --> 00:01:24.077 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>...He doesn't need you alive</i>
 <i>for what he has planned.</i>

00:01:29.849 --> 00:01:32.018 position:13% line:89% align:start
Until next time, Michelle!

00:01:32.051 --> 00:01:35.021 position:10% line:83% align:start
And stay out of trouble, our
dinner on Earth awaits!

00:01:35.054 --> 00:01:36.357 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groan]

00:01:36.390 --> 00:01:37.958 position:5% line:89% align:start
Sounds good!

00:01:37.992 --> 00:01:39.692 position:5% line:83% align:start
Friendly dinner for
three, can't wait!

00:01:40.027 --> 00:01:41.295 position:27% line:89% align:start
[unhappy groan]

00:01:43.030 --> 00:01:44.832 position:52% line:89% align:start
[nervous laugh]

00:01:45.299 --> 00:01:48.202 position:30% line:83% align:start
Well then It's gonna be
an awkward flight back.

00:01:48.235 --> 00:01:51.805 position:5% line:89% align:start
Yeah. If we survive long enough.

00:01:57.145 --> 00:02:01.950 position:41% line:77% align:start
(Bao)
Uh, General Aren't you
concerned about all of <i>them</i> ?

00:02:01.983 --> 00:02:05.120 position:10% line:83% align:start
Their numbers do not concern
me at the moment.

00:02:05.153 --> 00:02:06.688 position:7% line:89% align:start
They'll be dealt with in time.

00:02:06.721 --> 00:02:11.027 position:5% line:77% align:start
Once you have the First and the
Second in your sights, open fire
immediately.

00:02:11.060 --> 00:02:14.063 position:19% line:83% align:start
We'll bring 'em back,
dead or alive.

00:02:15.798 --> 00:02:18.435 position:33% line:89% align:start
O-kay then!

00:02:20.437 --> 00:02:23.072 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>How many more of you</i>
 <i>do I need to kill!?</i>

00:02:23.839 --> 00:02:29.079 position:16% line:83% align:start
Akari and Michelle, your
bodies will be mine!

00:02:29.913 --> 00:02:32.382 position:24% line:89% align:start
[fighting grunts]

00:02:33.383 --> 00:02:39.022 position:24% line:89% align:start
[fighting grunts]

00:02:39.056 --> 00:02:41.159 position:21% line:89% align:start
[grunt] Ivan! Do it!

00:02:42.994 --> 00:02:45.063 position:41% line:89% align:start
Right.

00:02:46.297 --> 00:02:51.403 position:10% line:77% align:start
Captain! The swarm is coming
from the direction of the
Annex 1!

00:02:51.936 --> 00:02:56.475 position:5% line:77% align:start
My guess is they're
trying to escape from Squad
4's little toxin girl.

00:02:57.443 --> 00:03:00.145 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:03:28.576 --> 00:03:31.479 position:35% line:89% align:start
[coughing]

00:03:42.291 --> 00:03:45.327 position:41% line:83% align:start
(Wolf)
Shhh.

00:03:46.295 --> 00:03:50.232 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Thinking)</i>
 <i>We don't have much time...</i>

00:03:50.265 --> 00:03:55.471 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>With the amount of toxic air</i>
 <i>we've been inhaling, we've only</i>
 <i>got about six minutes</i>

00:03:57.540 --> 00:03:59.175 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>I can do this...</i>

00:03:59.208 --> 00:04:01.144 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>...I can do this!</i>

00:04:03.413 --> 00:04:13.424 position:47% line:89% align:start
♪

00:04:13.457 --> 00:04:23.467 position:47% line:89% align:start
♪

00:04:23.500 --> 00:04:33.445 position:47% line:89% align:start
♪

00:04:33.478 --> 00:04:43.489 position:47% line:89% align:start
♪

00:04:43.522 --> 00:04:53.466 position:47% line:89% align:start
♪

00:04:53.499 --> 00:05:03.510 position:47% line:89% align:start
♪

00:05:03.543 --> 00:05:13.488 position:47% line:89% align:start
♪

00:05:13.521 --> 00:05:23.531 position:47% line:89% align:start
♪

00:05:23.564 --> 00:05:30.572 position:47% line:89% align:start
♪

00:05:32.474 --> 00:05:37.246 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>[computer glitching]</i>

00:05:37.279 --> 00:05:40.149 position:16% line:83% align:start
We only have six minutes
to hack the radio tower?

00:05:40.182 --> 00:05:42.184 position:21% line:83% align:start
There's just no way.
That's not enough time!

00:05:42.217 --> 00:05:43.385 position:5% line:89% align:start
I know...

00:05:43.419 --> 00:05:45.455 position:19% line:83% align:start
I've got this horrible
pit in my stomach.

00:05:45.488 --> 00:05:49.392 position:13% line:77% align:start
Like it's the night before
finals, and I've only just
begun to study.

00:05:49.426 --> 00:05:52.996 position:30% line:83% align:start
Trust me Amelia, I know
exactly how you feel.

00:06:00.236 --> 00:06:04.073 position:38% line:83% align:start
 <i>I... I always crack</i>
 <i>under pressure...</i>

00:06:04.107 --> 00:06:06.610 position:41% line:83% align:start
 <i>I've been that way</i>
 <i>my whole life.</i>

00:06:07.678 --> 00:06:11.582 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>In college, at work I</i>
 <i>could never keep up.</i>

00:06:13.752 --> 00:06:24.696 position:24% line:89% align:start
[employee chatter]

00:06:30.168 --> 00:06:31.169 position:55% line:77% align:start
Headed home?

00:06:31.203 --> 00:06:31.737 position:80% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:06:31.771 --> 00:06:32.971 position:35% line:77% align:start
Have a great weekend.

00:06:52.359 --> 00:06:54.561 position:24% line:89% align:start
[heavy breathing]

00:06:55.496 --> 00:07:01.502 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:07:02.704 --> 00:07:06.073 position:10% line:89% align:start
All my work just disappeared

00:07:06.708 --> 00:07:11.145 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>Tomorrow's my wedding day!</i>
 <i>There's no time!</i>

00:07:11.179 --> 00:07:14.182 position:30% line:89% align:start
[enraged yell]

00:07:14.215 --> 00:07:17.452 position:27% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Wolf Thinking)</i>
 <i>I couldn't do it on my own.</i>
 <i>There was no way to fix it.</i>

00:07:17.485 --> 00:07:19.254 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>...So I ran...</i>

00:07:21.724 --> 00:07:25.361 position:21% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Company President)</i>
 <i>Wolf, you idiot! What</i>
 <i>the hell have you done?!</i>

00:07:28.397 --> 00:07:30.699 position:5% line:83% align:start
He still submitted it
without fixing the bug?

00:07:30.733 --> 00:07:32.167 position:35% line:89% align:start
What was he thinking?

00:07:32.201 --> 00:07:35.739 position:5% line:77% align:start
Now the whole office is screwed
because he couldn't do his damn
job.

00:07:35.772 --> 00:07:40.510 position:41% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Wolf)</i>
 <i>The stress from it all made me</i>
 <i>physically ill; I had to quit.</i>

00:07:40.544 --> 00:07:44.080 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>It wasn't long before I fell</i>
 <i>into a deep depression.</i>

00:07:44.114 --> 00:07:47.217 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>My marriage fell apart, and my</i>
 <i>wife divorced me.</i>

00:07:47.250 --> 00:07:49.319 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'd never been more alone.</i>

00:07:51.388 --> 00:07:53.524 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:07:55.359 --> 00:07:57.695 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:08:13.478 --> 00:08:16.848 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>no It's not just because of me</i>

00:08:20.452 --> 00:08:27.727 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>I finally have the support</i>
 <i>of a real team. I have all of</i>
 <i>you.</i>

00:08:28.227 --> 00:08:31.197 position:61% line:83% align:start
(Ryuichi)
Wolf...

00:08:31.831 --> 00:08:38.237 position:27% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Wolf thinking)</i>
 <i>On Earth, we were nothing</i>
 <i>but a bunch of outcasts.</i>

00:08:38.271 --> 00:08:43.410 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>Skilled misfits given mediocre</i>
 <i>abilities and shipped to Mars</i>
 <i>to get our hands dirty.</i>

00:08:45.412 --> 00:08:48.515 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>But here</i>

00:08:53.220 --> 00:08:58.360 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>Together. We are more.</i>

00:08:58.393 --> 00:09:00.195 position:41% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Wolf)</i>
 <i>Okay everyone, this is it!</i>

00:09:02.130 --> 00:09:06.167 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>Nothing's gonna stop us from</i>
 <i>taking this tower back from</i>
 <i>those Squad 4 bastards.</i>

00:09:06.201 --> 00:09:09.772 position:21% line:77% align:start
 <i>It's time to restore</i>
 <i>communications between</i>
 <i>Earth and Mars!</i>

00:09:09.805 --> 00:09:16.245 position:7% line:71% align:start
 <i>If we can reach HQ back home,</i>
 <i>they may be able to dispatch a</i>
 <i>rescue unit before it's too</i>
 <i>late.</i>

00:09:16.278 --> 00:09:18.814 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>Once we tell them what Squad 4</i>
 <i>has really been up to,</i>

00:09:18.848 --> 00:09:23.319 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>it might put them in a position</i>
 <i>where they're forced to</i>
 <i>surrender.</i>

00:09:23.352 --> 00:09:26.556 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>We're really gonna</i>
 <i>pull this off.</i>

00:09:26.590 --> 00:09:30.293 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>We're gonna make it</i>

00:09:30.327 --> 00:09:33.296 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>If we don't, we all die.</i>

00:09:39.302 --> 00:09:41.371 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:09:46.978 --> 00:09:49.480 position:30% line:89% align:start
[bloody cough]

00:09:50.615 --> 00:09:54.887 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>I don't know how much</i>
 <i>more time I can buy them.</i>

00:09:54.920 --> 00:09:58.322 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>The toxin is working its way</i>
 <i>through me too quickly.</i>

00:09:58.356 --> 00:10:01.393 position:61% line:89% align:start
[small gasp]

00:10:01.427 --> 00:10:04.663 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groan]

00:10:04.697 --> 00:10:09.668 position:27% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Keiji thinking)</i>
 <i>When I lost my arm... The wound</i>
 <i>was exposed to bacteria.</i>

00:10:12.906 --> 00:10:16.910 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>[computer whirring]</i>

00:10:18.912 --> 00:10:20.246 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:10:20.280 --> 00:10:22.415 position:5% line:89% align:start
Don't stop...

00:10:23.050 --> 00:10:25.552 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:10:27.755 --> 00:10:31.592 position:30% line:89% align:start
No... not now!

00:10:32.760 --> 00:10:34.729 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Xi Thinking)</i>
 <i>How's he still alive?</i>

00:10:34.762 --> 00:10:40.801 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>If I had stayed out of my suit</i>
 <i>any longer, Hong's bacteria</i>
 <i>would have destroyed my central</i>

00:10:40.836 --> 00:10:43.071 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>nervous system leaving</i>
 <i>me paralyzed.</i>

00:10:43.105 --> 00:10:49.010 position:13% line:71% align:start
 <i>Had he not insisted on me</i>
 <i>covering up, I'd have been</i>
 <i>helpless, and he would've easil</i>
 <i>succeeded.</i>

00:10:49.044 --> 00:10:51.613 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>All without every</i>
 <i>laying a hand on me.</i>

00:10:51.646 --> 00:10:54.483 position:38% line:89% align:start
 <i>...Shit!</i>

00:10:54.917 --> 00:10:56.651 position:13% line:83% align:start
Wait! Where in the hell do
you think you're going?

00:10:56.685 --> 00:11:01.557 position:7% line:77% align:start
Huh? I'm gonna track down the
others The bacteria will finish
this one off soon enough.

00:11:01.591 --> 00:11:04.694 position:5% line:83% align:start
Come on, do us a favor and
kill him before you leave.

00:11:04.727 --> 00:11:07.463 position:5% line:83% align:start
can't protect Hong in
my current condition.

00:11:09.932 --> 00:11:12.836 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sigh]

00:11:16.907 --> 00:11:23.781 position:41% line:77% align:start
(Wolf)
I can't do this without you
guys. Stay with me!

00:11:23.814 --> 00:11:26.985 position:38% line:83% align:start
(Ryuji)
Keep it together, don't scream!

00:11:28.853 --> 00:11:32.824 position:7% line:83% align:start
You don't have to worry about
him. He doesn't have long.

00:11:32.857 --> 00:11:36.694 position:10% line:83% align:start
If the bacteria doesn't kill
him, the internal bleeding will.

00:11:36.728 --> 00:11:39.798 position:33% line:83% align:start
Are you willing to bet
Hong's life on that?

00:11:39.831 --> 00:11:43.501 position:30% line:83% align:start
If he's faking, and you
leave us here alone

00:11:43.535 --> 00:11:47.438 position:16% line:77% align:start
He'll kill us both, and gain
access to the communication
room,

00:11:47.472 --> 00:11:48.941 position:24% line:89% align:start
Just 'cause you got soft!

00:11:48.974 --> 00:11:51.076 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:11:54.013 --> 00:11:57.349 position:35% line:77% align:start
(Ryuichi)
If we try to kill that thing,
Squad 4 will hear us.

00:11:57.383 --> 00:12:00.020 position:5% line:77% align:start
But if we do nothing, it'll kill
us before we can get our signal
out.

00:12:03.123 --> 00:12:08.595 position:16% line:83% align:start
[grunt] You're right Bao
I'll finish him.

00:12:11.665 --> 00:12:13.466 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:12:14.168 --> 00:12:17.939 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sobs]

00:12:18.806 --> 00:12:19.807 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>[loud crash]</i>

00:12:19.841 --> 00:12:21.008 position:41% line:89% align:start
What?

00:12:21.042 --> 00:12:23.945 position:5% line:89% align:start
Shit.  They're already inside?!

00:12:24.979 --> 00:12:27.915 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:12:28.549 --> 00:12:32.620 position:21% line:83% align:start
We've come too far I
won't let you stop us!

00:12:32.653 --> 00:12:35.123 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'm gonna finish this,
once and for all!

00:12:35.157 --> 00:12:36.658 position:33% line:89% align:start
Understand!?

00:12:37.893 --> 00:12:41.997 position:21% line:89% align:start
[screaming in pain]

00:12:42.898 --> 00:12:45.400 position:24% line:89% align:start
[horrified gasps]

00:12:46.869 --> 00:12:49.706 position:41% line:89% align:start
Keiji!

00:12:50.740 --> 00:12:51.774 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:12:52.507 --> 00:12:54.844 position:27% line:89% align:start
[attack grunts]

00:13:00.450 --> 00:13:01.417 position:5% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:13:02.752 --> 00:13:05.789 position:10% line:89% align:start
[grunt] You sneaky bastards!

00:13:13.831 --> 00:13:17.768 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>[countdown beeping]</i>

00:13:19.737 --> 00:13:21.438 position:27% line:89% align:start
[attack grunts]

00:13:22.173 --> 00:13:25.010 position:10% line:89% align:start
Damnit! I don't believe it.

00:13:25.043 --> 00:13:26.711 position:35% line:83% align:start
He <i>really</i>
was faking it!

00:13:27.879 --> 00:13:29.514 position:5% line:89% align:start
Finish up!

00:13:30.216 --> 00:13:32.184 position:35% line:89% align:start
You okay?

00:13:32.218 --> 00:13:33.718 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:13:35.654 --> 00:13:37.455 position:5% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:13:37.489 --> 00:13:38.791 position:5% line:89% align:start
[scream]

00:13:38.824 --> 00:13:40.626 position:44% line:89% align:start
Jo!

00:13:40.660 --> 00:13:44.563 position:10% line:83% align:start
How in the hell is he still
standing?!

00:13:44.597 --> 00:13:47.033 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>...The impact from my punch</i>
 <i>should have killed him.</i>

00:13:51.838 --> 00:13:54.908 position:5% line:83% align:start
Hey asshole! What do
you think you're doing?

00:13:54.942 --> 00:13:57.244 position:5% line:77% align:start
You like picking
on defenseless
little girls?

00:13:57.277 --> 00:13:58.912 position:38% line:89% align:start
[growl]

00:13:59.579 --> 00:14:01.615 position:5% line:89% align:start
You'll pay for that!

00:14:02.549 --> 00:14:06.753 position:10% line:83% align:start
Th-This can't be happening.
Not when we're so close!

00:14:06.787 --> 00:14:09.924 position:7% line:83% align:start
Our simple masks are about to
become obsolete in 3 minutes.

00:14:09.958 --> 00:14:12.427 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>If we don't resume the hack,</i>
 <i>we'll never make it in time.</i>

00:14:13.861 --> 00:14:17.031 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>I can't let them take back</i>
 <i>control of the tower</i>

00:14:17.065 --> 00:14:21.971 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>ut if I don't deal with Keiji o</i>
 <i>that roach, I'll never be able</i>
 <i>to stop them.</i>

00:14:22.004 --> 00:14:27.776 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>And if I focus my attention on</i>
 <i>Keiji, overgrown pest will kill</i>
 <i>Hong the second I turn my back.</i>

00:14:27.810 --> 00:14:30.846 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Keiji thinking)</i>
 <i>We don't have time for this!</i>

00:14:30.879 --> 00:14:35.251 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>If I attack one, the other will</i>
 <i>kill my teammates without a</i>
 <i>second's hesitation.</i>

00:14:35.285 --> 00:14:38.021 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>What's it gonna be</i>

